        public static OneProject wrap()
        Wrap the editor entities in an instance of oneProject, for exporting or importing
        Returns:
        a OneProject entity with all the editor entities stored in it as 'floating' JPA entities that have not been persisted. These are purely transient objects which mediate between the editor and the database, and should not be managed or persisted
